;000528A5{$/THESE FOUR BRIDGES LINK=/GWANO'S KEY JUNGLE SUPPLY=/LINES. TAKE 'EM ALL OUT,=/CLEAN AND SIMPLE.+$/DON GWANO IS TRAINING NEW=/TROOPS AT THIS JUNGLE SITE.=/BLAST ALL SIX SHACKS TO=/PUT IT OUT OF BUSINESS.+$/DESTROY DON GWANO'S OIL=/SUPPLY AT THIS OUTPOST. HIS=/OIL TANKS ARE DEFENDED BY=/FLAK GUNS, SO BE CAREFUL.+$/GWANO WANTS TO FIND OUT WHO=/SUNK HIS FREIGHTERS. WASTE=/THESE PATROL BOATS BEFORE=/THEY DISCOVER OUR POSITION.+$/A DIVISION OF SCUD LAUNCHERS=/IS PREPARING TO STRIKE A=/PEACEFUL NEIGHBOR. MAKE SURE=/THAT THEY NEVER GET OFF THE=/GROUND.+$/THESE FLAK GUNS ARE MAKING=/IT TOUGH TO FLY OVER THE=/ENEMY. KNOCK THEM OUT AND=/WE'LL HAVE A CLEAN SHOT AT=/THEIR MOST VITAL TARGETS.+$/DON GWANO IS SETTING UP A=/SATELLITE NETWORK. TAKE OUT=/HIS DISHES AND IT WILL BE=/USELESS.+$/SOME OF THE JUNGLE TROOPS=/FLED THEIR WRECKED CAMP AND=/HAVE DUG IN ALONG THIS=/TRAIL. BLAST THEIR GUNS SO=/WE CAN FLY SUPPLIES OVER=/THE AREA.+$/WITH THEIR LAST FREIGHTERS=/SUNK, THE ENEMY IS TAKING NO=/CHANCES. THESE BARGES HAVE=/A FULL NAVAL ESCORT. SINK=/IT AND THEY'LL BE HURTING.+}#1072#1072
