;00052CD5{$/DON GWANO'S FORCES RECEIVE=/THEIR POWER FROM THESE=/GENERATORS. BLOW THEM UP TO=/PUT 'EM IN THE DARK.+$/THESE JUNGLE TROOPS ARE=/TOUGH. THE LAST OF THEM HAVE=/ERECTED A BASE IN A JUNGLE=/CLEARING. ALL OF THEIR=/BARRACKS ARE TO BE UNBUILT.+$/WITH SUPPLY LINES CUT OFF,=/LOCAL WEAPON PRODUCTION HAS=/DOUBLED. DESTROY THIS=/FACTORY COMPLEX, AND WE'LL=/CALL YOU HOME.+$/$WITH THEIR SATELLITES/=/USELESS, THE ENEMY IS USING=/THESE RADIO TOWERS TO=/COMMUNICATE. BLAST THEM AND=/THE ENEMY WILL BE SILENCED.+$/THIS CARRIER IS LOADED WITH=/PLANES AND CARGO. YOU CAN'T=/SINK HER, BUT YOU CAN=/DESTROY ALL AIRCRAFT AND=/SUPPLIES ON DECK.+$/THE ENEMY IS BUILDING TANKS=/FOR AN ASSAULT AGAINST OUR=/ALLIES. PUT THEIR TANK=/FACTORIES OUT OF BUSINESS=/FOR GOOD.+$/THIS TANKER WILL BE USED TO=/EXPORT OIL AND FUND THE WAR.=/SINK IT BEFORE IT RECEIVES ITS=/PAYLOAD, BUT WATCH OUT FOR=/DOCK DEFENSES.+$/THIS ARMY BASE IS A=/STRATEGIC HOTSPOT. DESTROY=/ALL BUILDINGS TO RENDER IT=/INOPERABLE.=/BE CAREFUL~3B~ GROUND DEFENSES=/WILL BE VERY TOUGH.+}#1029#1026
