@000530D7-00053508-00-6A
;000530D7{$/THIS SUB AND ITS ESCORT=/ARE SHADOWING OUR CARRIER.=/DUST THEM BEFORE THEY DUST=/US. WATCH OUT FOR ENEMY=/AIR SUPPORT.+$/ENEMY NAVAL FORCES ARE USING=/THESE ABANDONED OIL RIGS TO=/LAUNCH ASSAULTS. TAKE THEM=/OUT TO REDUCE THEIR=/OFFENSIVE RANGE.+$/ENEMY AIR POWER MUST BE=/NEUTRALIZED. BLAST THEIR=/HANGARS AND PLANES BEFORE=/THEY CAN DO MORE DAMAGE.+$/DON GWANO HAS HIS BEST=/SCIENTISTS WORKING ON=/BIOLOGICAL WEAPONS. DESTROY=/THEIR JUNGLE LAB~3B~ LEAVE=/NOTHING INTACT.+$/THESE DESTROYERS ARE=/POSITIONING TO STRIKE OUR=/FORCES. STRIKE THEM FIRST,=/BUT WATCH OUT FOR THEIR=/ROCKET LAUNCHERS.+$/DON GWANO'S SCIENTISTS ARE=/TRYING TO GAIN CONTROL OF A=/SATELLITE LASER. TRASH THEIR=/DISH OR WE'LL BE TOAST.+$/THESE SILOS ARE PROTECTED=/BY HARDENED BUNKERS. BLAST=/THE BUNKER TO EXPOSE THE=/SILO, THEN BLAST THE SILO.=/GOT IT?+$/THE ENEMY HAS AN UNDERGROUND/=/OIL PIPELINE. THIS PUMPING=/STATION IS THE ONLY PLACE WE=/CAN CUT IT OFF. HIT IT FAST=/AND GET OUT OF THERE.+$/THIS BASE IS HARBORING SUBS=/THAT WILL BE DEPLOYED=/AGAINST US. SINK THEM LIKE=/YOU SANK THE FIRST ONE.+}#1077#1074
