;00053509{$/WITH YOUR NEW WEAPONS, YOU=/SHOULD BE ABLE TO DESTROY=/THESE CARRIERS' CONTROL=/TOWERS. IT WILL GIVE US=/CONTROL OF THE SEA.+$/DON GWANO IS MINING HIS=/COASTAL WATERS TO KEEP US=/FROM FINDING HIM. SINK THE=/MINE SHIPS AND THE MINES.+$/WITH HIS ARMY BASE KNOCKED=/OUT, DON GWANO HAS SEIZED=/THIS CIVILIAN AIRPORT. BLAST=/ALL OF HIS PLANES AND=HANGARS.+$/THIS OIL FIELD IS THE LAST=/SUPPLY OF CASH FOR THE=/ENEMY'S FORCES. TAKE OUT=/THESE OIL RIGS TO CRIPPLE=/THEIR EFFORTS.+$/DON GWANO IS DESPERATE. HE'S=/READYING THESE PERFUME=/FACTORIES FOR LAUNCHING=/CHEMICAL WARFARE. BLAST THEM=/OR WE'LL BE SURROUNDED BY=/STINK CLOUDS.+$/THE REMAINING ENEMY TANKS=/HAVE BEEN GATHERED TOGETHER.=/THEY SHOULD BE SITTING DUCKS=/FOR AN ACE LIKE YOU.+$/THIS ISLAND BASE IS THE LAST=/ENEMY SEA FORCE. IT IS=/HEAVILY DEFENDED, BUT YOUR=/NEW WEAPONS SHOULD GIVE YOU=/ENOUGH FIREPOWER.+$/GWANO HAS KEPT A CHOPPER=/FORCE HIDDEN IN UNDERGROUND=/CAVERNS. DESTROY ALL OF=/THEIR LAUNCH PADS.+$/WELL, THIS IS IT - OPERATION=/BIG CHEESE. WE'VE LOCATED=/DON GWANO'S SECRET BASE.=/IT'S DEEP IN THE JUNGLE AND=/IS SURROUNDED BY HIS=/EXPERIMENTAL DEFENSES.%/IT'S A RISKY MISSION, BUT=/YOU'VE BEATEN THE ODDS SO=/FAR...PULL THIS MISSION OFF=/AND YOU'LL GO HOME A HERO.+}#1239#1239
