;000539E0{\\$/HELLO. I AM PROFESSOR=/NEWRON, AND I WILL BE=/INTRODUCING SEVERAL NEW=/WEAPONS AND REFINEMENTS AS=/THEY ARE DEVELOPED.%/TO MAKE THE F-14 AN ASSAULT=/PLANE, I HAVE ADAPTED THE=/SOVIET AS$/-$/X-$/10 LENIN AIR TO=/GROUND MISSILE TO ADD TO=/ITS ARSENAL.+$/YOU HAVE FLOWN WELL SO FAR.=/HERE ARE SOME NEW INVENTIONS=/TO HELP YOU...%/~64~F-18: THIS IS AN AIR-TO-AIR=/LASER THAT WILL DESTROY ANY=/PLANE. YOU MUST WAIT FOR IT=/TO RECHARGE AFTER EACH SHOT.%/~63~F-14: I'VE JUST COMPLETED A=/SPECIAL BACKFIRE GUN. IT CAN=/BE USED DURING YOUR GROUND=/ASSAULT.\$/HARRIER: I'VE INCREASED THE=/NUMBER OF HARDPOINTS. THIS=/WILL LET YOU CARRY MORE=/WEAPONRY.%$/I HOPE THEY WILL SERVE YOU=/WELL. GOOD LUCK.+$/WELCOME ABOARD. HERE ARE=/SOME NEW INVENTIONS TO HELP=/YOU.%/~64~HARRIER: THE THUNDERBALL=/WEAPON CAN DESTROY ALL=/VISIBLE AIRBORNE OBJECTS.=/IT TAKES A LONG TIME TO=/POWER UP.%\$/~63~F-14: I'VE INCREASED THE=/NUMBER OF HARDPOINTS. THIS=/WILL LET YOU CARRY MORE=/WEAPONRY.%/F-18: I HAVE ADAPTED THE=BACKFIRE GUN TO THE F-18.\$/HARRIER: I HAVE ADAPTED THE=/BACKFIRE GUN TO THE HARRIER.\}#1080#1068
