;00054223{$/I'M SURE THE TAX PAYING=/PUBLIC THINKS HIGHLY OF YOUR=/FLYING SKILLS.+$/YOU CHOWDERHEAD, YOU CRASHED!+$/THAT'S A 74 MILLION DOLLAR=/PLANE YOU TOOK FOR A DIP!+$/THAT WAS SUPPOSED TO BE A=/BOMBING RUN, NOT A CRASH=/COURSE!+$/WE ONLY HAVE ONE PLANE=/LEFT - YOU BETTER MAKE THIS=/ONE COUNT!+MR. PRESIDENT, WE'VE LOST A=PLANE. FORTUNATELY, THE=PILOT BAILED OUT IN TIME.+\MR. PRESIDENT, OUR ACE PILOT=IS MISSING IN ACTION. THERE=IS NO OTHER OPTION OPEN TO=US THAN TO PULL OUT=COMPLETELY.+\$/LOSE ANOTHER PLANE, AND=/YOU'RE TOAST!+$/OUT OF FUEL?!?!?^~14~=/THERE ARE NO GAS STATIONS=/IN THE SKY, BUDDY!+$/RUNNING AW~63~AY LIKE A CHIC~63~KEN=/WON'T WIN THE WAR. TRY A~63~GAIN.+$/YOU GOT 'EM ACE!!!^~14~=/LET'S KEEP 'EM ON THE RUN!^~FF~^~78~+I SEE- I'LL SEND MY PERSONAL=CONDOLENCES TO THE FAMILY.+$/I DIDN'T THINK IT WAS=/POSSIBLE, BUT YOU'VE MANAGED=/TO BEAT THE ODDS AND DEFEAT=/DON GWANO'S FORCES.+$/YOUR HEROICS HAVE EARNED YOU=/A PLACE IN THE HISTORY=/BOOKS. IT HAS BEEN AN HONOR=/TO SERVE WITH YOU.+$/IF THERE IS EVER ANOTHER=/CHALLENGE TO WORLD FREEDOM,=/I'M GLAD TO KNOW THAT WE=/CAN COUNT ON YOU TO DEFEND=/US.^~78~~64~+}#1122#1095
