;00054A71{IN THE WHITE HOUSE, AN=EMERGENCY MEETING IS CALLED=BY ADMIRAL CLIFF STORMDRANE.+$/MR. PRESIDENT, WE'VE GOT A=/MAJOR CONFLICT ERUPTING=/OVERSEAS.+$/THE BRUTAL DICTATOR, GENERAL=/DON GWANO, HAS ATTACKED HIS=/NEIGHBORS, USING HIS OIL=/MONEY TO FUND HIS ARMY AND=/NAVY.%/WE'VE GOT TO STOP HIM, BUT=/WE DON'T WANT TO LAUNCH A=/FULL OFFENSIVE.%/I PROPOSE THAT WE BEGIN A=/TOP SECRET MISSION USING OUR=/BEST PILOT WITH OUR NEWEST=/WEAPONRY. IN A SERIES OF=/LIGHTNING STRIKES WE CAN=/REMOVE THE THREAT OF GENERAL=/DON GWANO.+$/NOW WE'LL HEAR FROM=/PROFESSOR NEWRON, OUR=/WEAPONS EXPERT. HE WILL GIVE=/YOU A TECHNICAL REPORT.+$/THANK YOU, ADMIRAL. OUR=/PILOT IS THE BEST, AND HE'LL=/CHOOSE FROM OUR THREE BEST=/PLANES:^~64~=/THE FA-18 HORNET...\$/THE AV-8 HARRIER...\$/AND THE F-14 TOMCAT.\$/WE'VE ALREADY IMPROVED THEIR=/ARMOR, MAKING THEM VERY=/TOUGH TO DESTROY.%/I'M PREPARING TO INSTALL OUR=/LATEST WEAPONS, BUT IT WILL=/TAKE TIME. I WILL ADD THEM=/AS THEY ARE COMPLETED.+$/THANK YOU, PROFESSOR. WELL,=/MR. PRESIDENT, IS THE=/MISSION A GO?+}#1035#1032
